metadata.changes: Change 1: Replace sentence += f"{triple.subject} {triple.predicate} {triple.object}. " if i == 0 else f" and {triple.subject} {triple.predicate} {triple.object}." with 4 lines

diff_user.system:

<<<<<<< SEARCH
# Original code to find and replace (must match exactly, indentations and endlines as well)
=======
# New replacement code
>>>>>>> REPLACE

diff_user.user:
An incorrect diff format was detected in this change:
Here's an improvement suggestion focusing on better sentence structure and conjunctions for combining triples, particularly when they share the same subject:

```diff
<<<<<<< SEARCH
                    sentence += f"{triple.subject} {triple.predicate} {triple.object}. " if i == 0 else f" and {triple.subject} {triple.predicate} {triple.object}."
>>>>>>> REPLACE
                    if i > 0 and triples[i-1].subject == triple.subject:
                        sentence += f" and {triple.predicate} {triple.object}."
                    else:
                        sentence += f"{triple.subject} {triple.predicate} {triple.object}."
```

Please fix it to the correct format.
